{"tid":306093,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來支那人去到世界各地都會響香港人既朵","createTime":"2017-07-02T08:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T20:53:00.000Z","uid":51329,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5130062558c9459bd70aec69690ffd7a1f305a4e","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"岩岩去七星潭 俾一班人問路點去柴魚博物館<br />\n咁我話我都想去 睇緊google map點去<br />\n我以為佢地係台灣local<br />\n點知佢地同我講佢地係黎自香港<br />\n我即刻黑面用廣東話講我都係香港人<br />\n你班支那豬仲夠膽繼續向我講普通話<br />\n屌你老母 周圍用香港人既朵<br />\n佢地屙完既屎實係我地幫佢地抆屎啦屌<br />\n<br />\n依家無跟到佢地入博物館<br />\n自己去到睇海上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/164320_b6bbb41290d956ad463b70ecea66d221.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F164320_b6bbb41290d956ad463b70ecea66d221.jpg&h=cd9bceab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"068f131ac8b27696c2c00860cb5358a369162797","tid":306093,"uid":114097,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉<br />\n肯定有自知之明唔敢講自己係蝗<br />\n再唔係就腥香簡人<br />\n死開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd66b7bfc4ddc2bf53099de6619a9c55822ff379","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"聽到果下眼都突<br />\n心諗你都叫香港人<br />\n邊撚到香 睇過？"},{"pid":"e60b7815fffaf4f7e6361c4fab165be56fd19db4","tid":306093,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"支那人想用臭幾多個朵先安落？"},{"pid":"b46861d6e8afb7956c471033028309d13e946f07","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/165900_1013d0bc8edb3c9b3902673f3cb2bfe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F165900_1013d0bc8edb3c9b3902673f3cb2bfe8.jpg&h=690b98fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d57c0cb5f25916b5bc1b57b18e602c7f4e8beae","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"有無人陪我傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f825e44c8dbaac996c6199e741d0918a3f717ea3","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/171353_6470346bfcceced47694fc37e8133745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F171353_6470346bfcceced47694fc37e8133745.jpg&h=7897b79c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0f8c4bdcdc2afd117fdb1450c262ac2b1269667","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"走了<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/174013_e92831c5a92659cc3305bc1969de9962.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F174013_e92831c5a92659cc3305bc1969de9962.jpg&h=0c145f58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"666a69692331fa657da7b3a614ca4864fab9c7bd","tid":306093,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"佢地自知中國人個朵臭曬嘛"},{"pid":"9b9d2745238e7909df0a3e82e5c6a773c69e56ec","tid":306093,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"風景唔錯"},{"pid":"5c00a4f766d09aa910e08b02b5777a647ef81b01","tid":306093,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"成日都有五毛開post話香港人係中國人<br />\n<br />\n但係班蝗去到外國又要扮香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你地班蝗國仆街都知係兩個唔同種族<br />\n<br />\n五毛被蝗國旅客收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c367c74cd6ab38456399cf6634553be1339aa002","tid":306093,"uid":106429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:48:15.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母啦 影撚衰哂香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000dfd5bc9c6c0281e4663846d063239a6010d64","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地係抆屎民族"},{"pid":"3b032bbab4e75fda72b9086ec2cae8ffe0fa832b","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢老母啦 影撚衰哂香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日同人地講我係香港人都會覺得唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd022141dcb6191c7abbaecd7ebc90e9fd9fb28","tid":306093,"uid":22876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"就算唔尻認香港人<br />\n佢哋都寧願用地區黎自我介紹<br />\n例如來自上海北京廣東之類<br />\n<br />\n無計<br />\n因為中國人個名實在臭過屎坑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3111faaee892a96b618bbc3425c9f8915e5138","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算唔尻認香港人<br />\n佢哋都寧願用地區黎自我介紹<br />\n例如來自上海北京廣東之類<br />\n<br />\n無計<br />\n因為中國人個名實在臭過屎坑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c82e82d40914eaa057f768f71f058522a7c7fc","tid":306093,"uid":7355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"你估台灣人唔識分香港人同大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed740328a06f084d3bb31ae047678ce649544b7","tid":306093,"uid":54024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你估台灣人唔識分香港人同大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你估其他地方既人都一定識分香港人同大陸人？其實香港人個朵已經俾好多大陸人同腥港人搞臭晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02b579ac8a484fcf59c57d61853e55fb724fd2a","tid":306093,"uid":50789,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"大陸都有信徒，香港立國不遠矣"},{"pid":"8253688ea93cac242a4e4c50fd3add9318e1a911","tid":306093,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"香港個朵比佢地玩臭左之後就到新加坡 韓國 日本"},{"pid":"de3db575d1519740eb5a5709010daa0ce615f5d8","tid":306093,"uid":104474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸都有信徒，香港立國不遠矣</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過香港唔立國就算有幾多本passport都難保日後會無立足之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9f70c58a13c5e016eaffba3bcf88b544995753","tid":306093,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:09:36.000Z","msg":"去外國唔知認唔認香港人&hellip;"},{"pid":"bb1be12e5e5a222c3a6fd40a4daaa84a3511289f","tid":306093,"uid":51329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去外國唔知認唔認香港人&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n都唔知點介紹自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32522126b6ee704b4af5499e0b3377b0569bff8a","tid":306093,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"不過好多外國人識分廣東話同其他鄉下話，唔駛太擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690c181124e3f17c9b7949ff2b6f8510b2e1a2c6","tid":306093,"uid":104474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過好多外國人識分廣東話同其他鄉下話，唔駛太擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人連香港以前係英國都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}